    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/2bb8baae7c2bcbfdf391b9a1249ef46c.poster.avif?t=1727874010\" width=612 height=158 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/2bb8baae7c2bcbfdf391b9a1249ef46c.webm?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/2bb8baae7c2bcbfdf391b9a1249ef46c.mp4?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Biolum</strong> 以一项沉浸式任务为背景展开，带领观众进入海洋最深处，通过科学研究人员 Rachel 的视角探索海底深渊，由曾参与电视剧太空无垠的女演员 <strong>Dominique Tipper</strong> 配音。Rachel 由著名海洋科学家 Eva 指导，由曾参与电影沙丘的女演员 <strong>Charlotte Rampling</strong> 饰演。当我们探索这个流光溢彩的 VR 海底世界的奥秘时，很明显这其中的关系并不像我们想象的那么简单…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/d1eba097b143c0bf370a3cb451669b5d.poster.avif?t=1727874010\" width=612 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/d1eba097b143c0bf370a3cb451669b5d.webm?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/d1eba097b143c0bf370a3cb451669b5d.mp4?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寄生生物发光</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rachel 发现一种发光的寄生虫正在感染海洋动植物群。当Rachel和Eva试图理解其中科学原理时，各种不同的发光海洋生物在周围游来游去。美丽的发光生物正在对自然生态系统造成严重破坏。这是如何发生的，这意味着什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/721d436c0133905c5ab5443bb5950e82.poster.avif?t=1727874010\" width=612 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/721d436c0133905c5ab5443bb5950e82.webm?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/721d436c0133905c5ab5443bb5950e82.mp4?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不为人知的宇宙奇观</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个 VR 故事中，没有什么是像看起来那样。美丽的事物很快显现出惊人有传染性，而且可能比想象的更危险。当Rachel被这些寄生虫感染之后，她面临着一场为了她的生命而进行的催眠斗争。受深海生物之美的启发，<strong>Biolum</strong> 模糊了生物学真相和科幻之间的界限，并结合了存在主义主题和伟大未知的世界奇观。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/131bc3096d0c6d2d403d2b94819c1280.poster.avif?t=1727874010\" width=612 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/131bc3096d0c6d2d403d2b94819c1280.webm?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/131bc3096d0c6d2d403d2b94819c1280.mp4?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻巧的互动贯穿整个故事情节，并带领您感受Rachel的视角并沉浸在她的探索中</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Biolum</strong> 提供英语、法语和中文版本，是 30 分钟的互动和叙事体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >空间化身临其境的声音增强了深海的感觉以及周围危险和美丽的真实感</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>奖项</strong>：SXSW 观众奖、NewImages、UNIFRANCE 奖、Courant3D、VR 大奖</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/b86cf33a7cbe0e76e93c375dd2697c11.poster.avif?t=1727874010\" width=612 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/b86cf33a7cbe0e76e93c375dd2697c11.webm?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/b86cf33a7cbe0e76e93c375dd2697c11.mp4?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >导演：Abel Kohen，联合编剧：Jon Rowe和Abel Kohen。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由IKO、Reynard Films和prefrontal cortex制作。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由Astrea发行。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/c3ffb710f049b5633ba61fc8799e0351.poster.avif?t=1727874010\" width=612 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/c3ffb710f049b5633ba61fc8799e0351.webm?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1183700/extras/c3ffb710f049b5633ba61fc8799e0351.mp4?t=1727874010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
